title: Buff Headwear Headband Botanic
description: The Headband Buff is a quick and easy application to keep sweat and hair out of your face and eyes. With its four-channel wicking fibers, CoolMax Extreme fabric makes a great helmet liner and sweatband that will keep you cool and dry in hot months and can be slid over your ears in colder months for thermal protection.

title: CoverGirl Perfect Blend Pencil Basic Black(N) 100, (Pack of 2)
description: Our classic liner with blending power. For a defined look, draw a precise line; for a smoky look, softly smudge with the plush blender tip.

title: Maybelline Great Lash Waterproof Mascara, Very Black- .43 Fluid Ounce
description: Maybelline’s lash-doubling formula conditions as it thickens, making even tiny lashes 100% fuller and more healthy-looking. The lash-building brush builds full lashes with no clumps or globs. Available in five shades, in Washable, Waterproof, and Curved Brush.
